OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny start for many places,
OL,6,Falthough cloudier across southeastern
OL,7,Fareas at first. Through the afternoon
OL,8,Fcloud increases, but still some sunny
OL,9,Fintervals occur, followed by sunny
OL,10,Fperiods for this evening. Light
OL,11,Fonshore breezes will keep coasts
OL,12,Fslightly cooler than inland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FLargely clear, with only a
OL,15,Flittle patchy cloud, and light winds
OL,16,Faway from the north Kent coast. Also
OL,17,Fbecoming cooler than many recent
OL,18,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
