OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAreas of cloud for the morning
OL,6,Fand at first in the afternoon, then
OL,7,Fmost places gradually becoming sunny.
OL,8,FRather warm or warm for most places,
OL,9,Fhighest temperatures across Hampshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FRemaining warm with light winds and
OL,13,Fdry. Possibly cloudy at times Monday
OL,14,Fand Tuesday, then Wednesday sunnier
OL,15,Fconditions are likely.
